headline: These 3 stocks are 'great buying opportunities,' CIO says
summary: Blanke Schein Wealth Management chief investment officer Robert Schein joins Market Domination Overtime with Josh Lipton to discuss three stock picks he thinks are "buying opportunities": D.R. Horton (DHI), Apple (AAPL), and Advanced Micro Devices (AMD). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.
